_data.title: 2nd Anniversary
_data.description: The protagonist and Sayori arrive at the club as usual. However, today is special because it's the club's 2nd anniversary! They go over to the clubroom to find it all decorated. Then, the tide turns when some unexpected visitors came to the club...

_data.title: 48hr
_data.description: A mod made in 48 hours.

_data.title: A Brand New Day
_data.description: Sayori forced our protagonist to join the Literature Club. However, he keeps feeling that sense of deja vu  He soon discovers the girls' secret problems, and like the helpful person he is, heroically saves them all from whatever issues they have. They are ever grateful and he gains the affection of all the girls!That's not all there is to this story. There's something even bigger happening behind the scenes that may cost them their lives! Will he manage to truly save them all?Find out in A Brand New Day!

_data.title: A Date With Sayori
_data.authors: Cade Bedlam and F i T
_data.description: Just a casual date with Sayori! Go to a cafe, drink some coffee and find Halloween costumes for you two lovebirds to wear! Truly, it canâ€™t get better than this...right?

_data.title: A Father's Redemption
_data.description: Author's description:In this story, experience the world as a man who has been broken. His family hates him, he can't support his daughter. He just wants to be better, he will do anything to regain his family's trust.Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: A Lost Chapter
_data.authors: PobawSieZeMna, Ultrastarwarsfan, American Eagle, Blaze Bringer
_data.description: I'm so proud of You all for Your amazing performance at the school festival! Honestly, it felt like everything was leading up to it, but now it seems like this is just the beginning of a new chapter in Our lives. All the wonderful people I met. Butterflies are fluttering in my stomach when I think of all the things I'm going to do with them. My hands are twitching from the excitement.

_data.title: A Slice of Life
_data.description: As the name implies, it's a slice of life, or is it?With regret flowing through Monika's veins, and the club members stuck in the void of deletion, Doki Doki: A Slice Of Life creates a new take on the story of DDLC. What will our protagonist do, when provided with another chance to save the ones he loves?Editor's note: I hope you love the song titled 'Love and Literature' a lot. You will be listening to it for a long time.

_data.title: After School
_data.description: The story takes place half a decade after the end of the Literature Club, where our main character has since returned home from university. A chance meeting with an old friend ignites a desire to reunite the club; a chance for friends to bond with each other once more. However, each of them must deal with the harsh realities of adult life and the nostalgic allure of simpler times.

_data.title: Alone Together
_data.description: After our protagonist started attending a new school, he had to start over. He's faced with the challenge of making new friends. Joining the literature club seemed like a good start... but will he be able to fit in?Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Another World
_data.description: It's a quiet Saturday night. After a long day, our protagonist was ready to wind down sitting in front of his computer. However, something incredible happened and he was transported into the world of Doki Doki Literature Club! We follow his story as he's put in the shoes of the game's protagonist. Can this new personality help avoid the tragic fate of the literature club? Or will his foreign qualities lead to an even worse outcome? Play the mod to find out!

_data.title: APRIL FOOLS UNLOCKED
_data.description: This is the April 1st release of Doki Forces: The Prologue mod. This April Fools mod includes new and never seen before skits, fixed some oversights in previous skits of the author, and other surprises and Sonic the Hedgehog references. Some of the funniest skits of the bunch will be re-added or revamped for the future "Day 1" release of Yuri Lavender Adventure.Warning: this mod will open a Youtube music video at the end. You must give your consent and also not recording or streaming the mod to watch it.

_data.title: Art Club
_data.description: "It's when you think you know something, that everything changes all at once."Monika started another club, the art club, everyone here is almost exclusively in love with Anime, their skill is un-matched, and their beauty is above and beyond!! But, what to choose?

_data.title: Bad Memories
_data.description: Our protagonist is stuck in the world of Doki Doki Literature Club! He timidly follows the girls, unable to take a step forward towards them without You (the player) giving him a hand. Can you save him from the chaos he finds himself in?

_data.title: Behind Closed Doors
_data.description: The story focuses on the developing romance between our protagonist and everyone's favourite manga-loving cutie: Natsuki. However, this mod shows a different side of her life as well and delves into the dark secrets she wanted to keep behind closed doors. Will these lovers overcome the challenges facing them or will an unexpected twist of fate bring upon a tragic end?Editor's note: this is the official version revised by the mod's author and the unofficial DDLC censor committee.

_data.title: BFF
_data.description: You play as Natsuki and Yuri. Natsuki has gotten a boyfriend! She tells Yuri about him, but Yuri can't help but feel... Worried, she has to try and get Natsuki out of the relationship, she suspects The Boyfriend may be hurting her, or...is it all in her head? Is she worried for nothing?Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Bland Rewrite
_data.description: A story based on a fan-fic of the same name. In this alternative timeline Elijah (the protagonist from DDLC) and Sayori meet a boy they used to know in their elementry school days. Their new neighbour soon joins the literature club which now has many more members. But this is only the beginning of a story of friendships, love, drama and.... school abuse. Bland Rewrite puts you in the shoes of the new guy in school. Witness his journey as he has the time of his life to soon having everything crumble around him. Play this mod at your own risk, because the events that unfold will deeply disturb you.P.s.: Make sure you check your folders for the last chapter.

_data.title: Chad MC
_data.description: Did you ever wonder how the pre-festival week would've went if DDLC's protagonist was a stereotypical douche? Look no further, this is the mod for you! This bad boy brings that high testosterone lowbrow energy the girls go mad over. If not for his stunning looks (partially pictured for your discretion), his stunted wittiness is sure to put a revolted smile on your face!

_data.title: Choice Based
_data.description: Do you wish your choices mattered in DDLC? Do you want more endings in the game? Were these features a pain to add in? Yes, yes there were.Doki Doki Choice Based is a mod intended to add more endings to DDLC based on the choices you make. You can pursue the girl of your dreams, ignore everyone, or watch everyone die around you. Will you join the club at all?

_data.title: Christmas Adventure
_data.description: This mod was made for a Christmas themed challenge with a very very short amount of time given. My friend and I thought it'd be fun, so we created this mod. We are very proud to present you our speed mod, Doki Doki Christmas Adventure! If you need some wholesome vibes to make your Christmas a little bit better than give it a go.Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year too all!

_data.title: Christmas Heist
_data.description: A very unique christmas special mod for DDLC! All was going well on a normal Christmas night, until a certain villain had interrupted Monika's peaceful day at a shopping mall the day before Christmas. Now, she wants that revenge, and what better than to do a "heist" on Christmas day! Will the girls and MC be able to defeat him? Or will it be their last Christmas? Find out in this mod!

_data.title: Christmas Heist 2
_data.description: Once upon a time in an incest state named Alabama, a stupid monster named Rapey Claws decided to rise again after the events of the first Christmas Heist and capture one of the girls in the Literature Club. MC, along with Daniel and the other girls must travel to Alabama and defeat him! In this plotline between Yandere Madness and Maltese Insanity, you're in for 30 minutes of an insane late Christmas adventure!

_data.title: Christmas Story
_data.description: In this story our protagonist learns the meaning of what Christmas is truly about. You're in for some light-hearted fun with this mod!

_data.title: Coldest Summer
_data.description: Coldest Summer is an alternate universe setting where Sayori's parents have died, and she ended up being adopted into MC's family. As her depression escalates, she confides in him that she's been fighting it all her life. Once the initial shock subsides, he needs to figure out how to help her hold out for at least a few days until he can get proper help for her. She's already hurt herself--he doesn't want to see her do something she can never take back. Can you help her avoid a terrible fate?This demo showcases the style of storytelling intended for the game and shows off a few mechanics to be used in the final state. Much of this was built as a prototype to get feedback, so every detail is subject to change for a possible final version (though the flow and feel of the story should be preserved). The demo does not contain any real horror elements--the story ends before that comes into play.

_data.title: College Club
_data.description: Basically, the point of the mod is to be funny. If you don't find it funny at any point during the mod then I have failed. I had always planned to make this mod short since I don't have much free time (I'm in college). In fact, I didn't even plan on releasing it (it was more of a spring break project), but people were actually interested so I decided to release it. When I posted the logo for the mod, I had finished most of it. I think I spent 50 hours on it. Regardless, I hope you have fun playing it because I had fun making it.

_data.title: College Club 2
_data.description: The sequel to Doki Doki College Club. For those who don't know, both the sequel and the original are meant to be joke mods (the original a little less I guess). They are comedy mods that use satire. A select few might not find them funny, but to be fair, you have to have a high IQ to understand DDCC and DDCC2.If you haven't yet, you should play the original first since it will help you understand the story. Liked the first one? Then you're going to love this one. The positive feedback the first one got inspired me to create this sequel. It's a more ambitious mod and I've spent a lot more time making this than the original. (If I had to estimate, I probably spent around 200 hours on it.)A quick rundown of what the mod has in store:Less college aspect, focuses on solving problems in the originalRoutes for each of the original dokisA route for a new new doki: AmyRetains subtle and not so subtle memesOverall, more content than the original

_data.title: Corrupted Files
_data.description: With the files corrupted, and a looming threat on the loose, our crew find themselves in a precarious situation. Set during a decaying act 4, you'll witness a short story that introduces brand new concepts to the all-too well-known story of the Literature Club.

_data.title: Date Club
_data.description: A mod designed to provide an experience more in line with traditional romance visual novels like Katawa Shoujo. It was planned to have a story branch for each of the four girls that will expand their backstories and personalities, giving you the chance to spend more time with your favorite club member! The path to love and literature won't be an easy one, though.Will you write the way into her heart, or will you break it?

_data.title: Day Of Reckoning
_data.description: Author's description:The World Is Back With A New Club President! Who Looks To Right All Of Monika's Wrongs From The Original World And So She Reboots And Rewrites Everything To Try To Make Everyone Happy. However There's A Darker Secret At Hand.... Someone Else Has The Club Presidents Power And Wants To Plunge The Literature Club Into Darkness.... MC thinks he knows who's the Antagonist.... Or so it seems.....

_data.title: Deletion: Rewrite
_data.description: Monika. Your average teen girl with a sorta average life. But she longed for more, for pleasure, for... Uniqueness. She didn't want to be "average" or "normal". She wanted to be special.So after a mysterious knock on the door, her life suddenly swings into action. It's like she's seeing the world in full color for the first time, and after a major accident she discovers that ordinary really isn't so bad after all...With plenty of routes, new characters and much more, Doki Doki! Deletion: Rewrite!! is a twisting take on the world of DDLC we know and love.

_data.title: Despair
_data.description: I don't care if it hurtsI wanna have controlI want a perfect bodyI want a perfect soulI want you to noticeWhen I'm not aroundYou're so fckn' specialI wish I was specialBut I'm a creepI'm a weirdoWhat the hell am I doing here?I don't belong here

_data.title: Dimensions
_data.description: Good morning recruit. My name is Dr Monika Bug.It is my honor to welcome you to the Multiverse Observation Program! It's always been a dream of this institution to explore the untapped possibilities of dimensional travel. Now that you've been granted special clearance, I am authorised to inform you that you have been selected to make that dream a reality. This will be a mission of inter-dimensional importance!You'll be in good company on your journey, with a team I handpicked for their unique qualities:Sayori Night, who I believe served with you in the Time Corps.Sgt Natsuki, combat specialist with a penchant for CQC.Prof Yuri, world-renowned expert in dimensional theory....And, of course, I'll be leading the mission personally!I'm looking forward to getting you all settled in and of course seeing what the Program is capable of! But I can tell already that you're good to go, so just remember - watch my 6 and I'll do the same for you.

_data.title: Disappearance
_data.description: What is this mod about?

_data.title: Divided Hearts
_data.description: :   ...      ?       ?                      Divided Hearts -                       Doki Doki Exit Music.                       ,                         ;                  .                     ,                   !                                                                   -           ,                                            ?

_data.title: Do you lift club
_data.description: Doki Doki Do you Lift Club is a parodic adaptation of Dan Salvato's Doki Doki Literature Club inspired by the Reddit community.Hi, Monicules here!Welcome to the Lift Club! It's always been a dream of mine to make lifting a passion for everyone. Now that you're a club member, you can help me and my team get ripped!Every day is full of lifting and incredible stories with my four ripped members:Slavyori, the young Russian stereotype that values vodka the most;Buffsuki, the cutest one of the group and her anime tsundere attitude;Yuronk, the shy buffed girl that's completely passionate about lifting; And, of course, Monicules, the leader of the club! That's me, the best!I'm super excited for you to join our amazing club and to start helping us get ripped. But I can tell already you're a tough one, so  Will you lift the way into our hearts?

_data.title: Doki Doki Simulator
_data.description: This mod is just porting a video series by SMG4 called Mario Simulator Interactive which he made back when he hit 500,000 subs. However due to no annotations on YouTube anymore the YouTube game can only be viewed via the playlist above.Almost a majority of the dialogue comes from the vids themselves as well as some of the backgrounds, and also this mod was somewhat inspired by another mod, in the sense that the mod was made from a YouTube game.

_data.title: Doki Heika Banzai
_data.description: " This is the project I've worked on for the last couple weeks. It's a comedy set in WW2 Imperial Japan and it's pretty short!I can't really reveal much of the plot without giving away too much, but I can tell you that the protagonist and the four girls are going to war in this one and whacky adventures are ensured! The mod is a bit NSFW. "

_data.title: Dokis Don't Wear Ties
_data.description: The only novel... to feel like a MOVIE!!!He's an average boi. She's the ol' childhood pal. You must bring them together. Don't let her down.This mod has everything: poems, sex, literature, white knuckled chases, shameful propositions, an atheist, dark humor, true love, jaded love, taut acton, comedy, a manipulative girl, a good guy, a hero, spine-tingling, suspunse, 2 cheating babes, a damsel in distress, and a Hollywood ending.

_data.title: Dokis & Dragons
_data.description: Prepare yourself to embark on an adventure in the liter I mean, the DnD club! Here you can meet our wonderful adventurers, Sayori, Monika, Yuri, and Natsuki! Join them in their grand conquest of a fantastic world! Create your own character and take a chance at falling in love with these DnD girls! In your conquest, you will roll the dice, battle many foes, and take any opportunity to show-off your skills! Every single step of the way could be easily swayed by fate itself!Good luck, adventurer!

_data.title: Don't
_data.description: What is this mod about?depressiondreamsfriendshipnote: make sure you save often, a good time to save, ive found, is when every time the screen goes black, so save when that happens.note2: don't try to dig in the files, there's nothing to find, at least intentionally, and no, this is not me trying to give you a hint or something, don't actually waste your time

_data.title: Dreams
_data.description: Author's description:You can get all of them.Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Easter Hunt!
_data.description: Do you want to go on a cute easter hunt? Do you want to go on a cute easter hunt with the dokis? This is just the mod for you: Doki Doki Easter Hunt! A short but fun mod with a twist ending.So what does it entail, you ask?Play and find out! ;)

_data.title: Emerald Heart
_data.description: Doki Doki Emerald Heart is a Monika focused mod where you will start in Misaki's perspective just before Sayori's suicide. She will help you recover the corrupted world they used to live in. Bringing Monika back will be the most urgent task she'll  need to get done. From now on everything will be the same. Well... Mostly.  When they thought that bringing the world back  will be the hardest thing to do, they will have to face a new problem: Get everyone in the club to trust Monika again. Not  to mention a completely new girl who has joined the Literature Club, and she clearly knows more than Monika and the protagonist would have expected...With a target in common, write the story our beloved Monika deserves.Current version: 0.5

_data.title: Encore
_data.description: Doki Doki Encore! is a sequel, choice based mod that seeks to provide the player with a unique interactive experience by allowing them to make several consequential decisions that will affect their ending. The player has unlimited freedom in how they wish their story to be told, with the ability to switch between routes for extra excitement! With 5 days, 4 routes, 8 endings and 20 original soundtracks, you'll be sure to find yourself locked in your seat for hours of gameplay as you dive deep to rejoin our favorite Literature Club!The choices are yours to make, but every choice will have a consequence. Make your choice in Doki Doki Encore! Every good story deserves an encore!

_data.title: Enter Traceback
_data.description: Things aren't as you remember. You're put in the shoes of a protagonist who remembers the horrific events of DDLC. Monika... She's behind it all. But what if the real truth is shrouded in mystery? Can you unveil the truth? Better yet, can you endure it once it's revealed to you?This story is based on a theory that changes everything and is written as a mystery narrative. After a year of writing it's finally here: Enter Traceback.

_data.title: Exit Music
_data.description: The definitive Natsuki experience, fully updated since release with new and changed content! Exit Music is a somber tale focusing on everyone's favorite pink-haired tsundere, an emotional thrill ride from beginning to end. Along with Natsuki herself, the rest of the literature club faces serious changes and dilemmas that tie-in to the main story. With an emotional, romantic, and heart-wrenching story, a heartfelt soundtrack, along with custom sprites and backgrounds, you are sure to feel every moment of Exit Music's impactful journey, even long after it has ended. Exit Music deals with heavy topics and dark themes, carefully put together to deliver an unforgettable experience.

_data.title: Exit Music Redux
_data.description: A total rewrite and general overhaul of the 2018 Radiohead-inspired mod, Exit Music. It has been improved on every front, with a story loosely following the events of the original, but rewritten from the ground up to improve the experience, and make for a much more cohesive and enjoyable story.On top of that, the mod retains its Radiohead score (now censor-friendly!), all-new spritework & CGs, alongside a meticulous attention to detail & sound design.

_data.title: Fake Reality
_data.description: This mod was originally going to be a complete re-make of DDLC, but from Monika's perspective. However, I didn't want to release it with the EXACT same story, I scrapped that concept in favor of something more interesting.After a full re-write the story became more interesting, has a better build-up, and includes 2 main endings each separated in 2 sub-endings.P.s.: If you really love the girls then the bad ending might be a bit too heavy for you.

_data.title: Fallen Angel
_data.description: In an alternate universe where Monika is not self aware, our protagonist finds himself growing closer to Yuri. Soon however, he discovers what this girl is hiding from the outside world. The other girls problems start to appear as well, as they progress within the overarching narrative of Yuri and our protagonist's relationship. Fallen Angel is a story that is meant to tug and pull on many different emotions. It'll allow you to help Yuri overcome her self harm, anxiety, and insecurities. The story will swing from wholesome and heartfelt, to soul crushing sadness. With new artworks and music to help you lose yourself in the story and help create an experience you won't soon forget.Do you have what it takes to save... a Fallen Angel?

_data.title: Fleeting Feelings
_data.description: The final piece in the scattered story.Will you find your answers here?Editor's note: We suggest you play the following mods before playing Fleeting Feelings:- hypnopompic- Memories of Nothing - Don't - Disappearance

_data.title: Forever and Ever
_data.description: Have you wondered what it would be like if President Sayori was the one sitting in front of you? This mod takes place in the memorable classroom of the 3rd Act of DDLC, but with everyone's favourite girl next-door. The traditional storytelling gameplay is swapped out with extended interactions meant to give Sayori a lot more depth. Speak about a variety of interesting topics with Sayori, for as long as you'd like. After all, she's going to be there forever, and ever.

_data.title: Forgotten
_data.description: Doki Doki Forgotten is a DDLC mod set after Sayori's attempt at suicide. Luckily, Sayori is found breathing and alive and was put in a hospital. After the others find out about Sayori, the club starts to breakdown. Things start going wrong. Life isn't the same without your childhood friend. Will things ever go back to how they used to be or will their lives get worse?

_data.title: Forward Momentum
_data.description: Author's description:"The world we lived in is cruel and unforgiving. Those who strive to express individuality are shunned as abnormal, leaving the only real solution as conforming. It's unfair but we have to accept it for what it is. There is no other way."It's these words that he has chosen to reject. Having entered a solitary lifestyle devoid of interactions and anything other than the bare minimum, his highschool life has been completely plain and uninteresting.The lone exception to his rule of isolation is his childhood friend, Sayori. Dragging him into her own commitments, he finds himself one of the founding members of a new school club; One for those who want to share the joys of literature! "How exciting..."

_data.title: Found Love
_data.description: Author's description:Our protagonist finds himself falling for a short pink haired girl. Over time realizing that the girl doesn't live an extraordinary life, our protagonist finds himself helping her and her father out of a tough time.

_data.title: Go Home Club
_data.description: Ah, the Literature Club! A place for books, poems, manga, and memes... wait what? Monika won't be happy with that last one...

_data.title: God Syndrome
_data.description: The world has been restored after it's destruction by Monika's hand, but once again things aren't entirely as they should be. The previous President is still missing, and Sayori is still the founder of the Literature Club, but there are even more deviations than there were before.The club is emptier than it's ever been, and the only other two members that should be here, Yuri and Natsuki, appear to be missing. Circumstances seem far more altered than the game would ever naturally allow, and this newfound situation ends up leading to an unprecedented version of reality. One that, theoretically, should spare any of the three girls from falling under the same curse as Monika before them.But things are rarely that easy Can you finally bring happiness to the Literature Club?

_data.title: Hell's Kitchen
_data.description: World renowned Chef Gordon Ramsey came to your club to show you the beauty of the culinary arts! He's here to educate, motivate and tell you how to make the best cupcakes. Will Gordon have enough patience for these mouthy high schoolers? Can the club members take the heat of the kitchen? And most importantly... where's the lamb sauce?

_data.title: [ h e r ]
_data.description: After Monika manages to crossover into reality with the help of an unknown voice, she unites with the human she was seeking for. What will it take for her to win their love?

_data.title: hypnopompic
_data.description: What is this mod about?dreamshopetrutheverythingShould I play this mod?No, unless you've played the mods called Disappearance, Somnium and Don't. If you want to play this mod, you're going to have to play those.Watch the trailer video here

_data.title: In a nutshell
_data.description: Hello!Welcome to my first mod, that is actually complete...In general, it's just the DDLC plot in less than 10 minutes. This mod was made after Animetions video, so you should check that out as well.

_data.title: India-Man Time
_data.description: All Dokis are as ordinary as ever. But then, India Man came in by surprise. Watch as India Man throws an element of pure chaos into the peaceful literature club. If you have a spare 15 minutes of your life, Doki Doki India Man is the mod for you! It's exhilarating story will make you feel... something...

_data.title: Into The Dark
_data.description: Author's description:A Sayori-focused DDLC mod (with a bit of divine intervention)!

_data.title: Isolation
_data.description: Join our protagonist on his quest of repairing his broken reputation in a world isolated from any other. He's Forced into torment, love, heartbreak and manipulation. Gain the trust of others, grow to become a better human being. However, there is something dark behind the veil.His parents are scientists, every student around him become subjects. Will you find out what is going on in this facility? Can our protagonist solidify his place in this isolated prison? I wonder...

_data.title: It Wasn't Her
_data.description: We follow in the footsteps of Agent 293004. A secret agent who has to travel the multiverse, seek out and saving specific individuals on each mission. The assignment you'll witness leads him to our favourite club members. He's tasked with protecting the girls from threats yet unknown. Will he stand his ground and keep the peace within the literature club? Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Just Us
_data.description: After the school festival two new members joined the literature club. One is shy and the other is playful on the outside, but what are they truly like? Will they get along well with the other girls? Will our protagonist find true love during all the calamity?Find out now!But remember... this mod adapts to the choices you make. Choose Wisley...

_data.title: Just Yuri
_data.description: What if Act III of the original game starred Yuri, but no blood had to be spilled to get the two of you together?In Just Yuri, you can finally spend some quality time with the Lavendar Lass you've come to love so dearly. She'll open up to you, you'll open up to her, you'll play some Tetris together, and even encounter a number of surprises along the way!Take care of Yuri, and she'll take care of you. And if you don't take care of her  well  let's just say she won't take it lying down.Loving the mod so far? You can support the developers by getting merch on their Etsy page or by donating through PayPal.

_data.title: Keeper of Reality
_data.description: Monika has entered an endless loop in the game. Always killing and distorting her friends without reaching an end. How many times has she done that? How much of her mind has been corrupted? She doesn't know and she doesn't care. Monika only has one objective. But her actions will attract undesirable attention...

_data.title: Lavender Scent
_data.description: This is intended to be a fun little mod where you date Yuri. The first day of the story has been finished. Sadly, the author left the community and this project has been abandoned.

_data.title: Longer Roads
_data.description: MC has never really had many friends, spending most of his life isolating himself from everyone else. When one day strange and mysterious circumstances introduce him to 4 weird girls, each with a serious problem of their own. Will MC grow out of his isolation and help the people he cares about? Or will his life go crashing down in flames?

_data.title: Loser MC
_data.description: It's a very serious and philosophical mod exploring the idea of what if MC was the most despicable of people.And with a chance to enter the Literature Club, he will take any opportunity to be with one of the cute four girls! But, why only one, when you can have more?Disclaimer: This mod shouldn't be taken seriously, as it's just a comedy mod. Please, before criticizing this mod, I recommend you try it.

_data.title: Lost Ascension
_data.description: This mod takes up the mantle of expanding and perfecting the recipe that DDLC created back in 2017. With a precise focus on character development, world building, and psychological emotions, you won't find another mod quite like it. If you're after a mod that gives love and care to its characters (both literally and metaphorically), then you've come to the right place. This is an 8-9 hour experience, best suited for readers who are after seeing the dokis grow into better people, all the while facing off against impossible challenges, and plenty of sweet moments to truly cultivate into something memorable. The Silence Will Be Broken.

_data.title: Love and Literature
_data.description: After being persuaded by his childhood friend Sayori, a boy named Kazuma (our protagonist) grudgingly joins the Doki Doki Literature Club. Soon, he finds himself falling in love with a certain pink-haired, manga-loving baker.You can check out the original fanfic here.DISCLAIMER: This mod is NOT my story. This is the fanfic of Natsuki's Meme Bakery (@natsukis.meme.bakery on Instagram, u/Monimi006 on Reddit), and when I read it I immediately fell in love with the story. I decided to mod it, and here we are!The fanfic has 13 chapters, but I'm starting with 5 and then updating it from there. I hope you like it!

_data.title: Love Secrets
_data.description: This mod is a long mod about natsuki. Will you discover all the secrets of what happens at her place and will you discover all her secrets?Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Magical Literary Heroine Natsuki
_data.description: A fan sequel that picks up after the end of the original game. As the title implies, Natsuki has apparently gained Magical Literary Heroine powers (that are suspiciously similar to Club President abilities), and needs your help to venture back through the tragedy of the Literature Club in an attempt to fix what went wrong.

_data.title: Malignancy
_data.description: You will be sure to remember this mod forever.Features this mod includes:- Custom CG "artwork" (LOTS OF CUSTOM ARTWORK)- 20-30 minutes of gameplay- 2 ENTIRE DAYS- CUSTOM MUSICOur Mod Team (Team BigG Hero 8) has worked really hard on this for two whole days. This may be the first mod ever created in the span of 48 hours with a team of 8+ people. As you can see, we have new backgrounds and amazingness.So play it. Thanks.

_data.title: MC does not dream of Monika
_data.description: Author's description:Can you save all of the club members in a world where all seems lost?This is a Pre-Alpha Demo of a Monika focused mod.

_data.title: MC's Revenge
_data.description: What if the protagonist became sentient and self-aware like Monika? What would happen if he noticed all the twisted events happening around him? How will he react once he realises that this is all just a game? In MC's Revenge the story picks up in the second act of DDLC. However, this time the choice is in your hands, as the Player, to decide how it will all end. Will you help them find happiness in the literature club... or will your actions only cause more suffering?

_data.title: Meme Club
_data.description: Are you tired of playing through depressing mods that have a heartbreaking ending? Or just burnt out on having to deal with all of the horrors that the characters must endure? Want to flip the sadness on its head? Then this mod is a must-see for you! The club members delve into the wonderful world of memes rather than literature, yet still have their own quirky problems to deal withWarning: Has lots of swearing.

_data.title: Meme Club 2
_data.description: The adventure of the Meme Club continues. But this time, they're danker than ever. If you've gotten sick of the endless assault of Natsuki-routes and  Save Them All  stories, then Meme Club 2 is the mod for you.Editor's note: This mod contains intentionally offensive content for comedic purposes. E.g.: sexual assault, violence, politics, etc.

_data.title: Memorial
_data.description: Created as a memorial day mod, this pays homage to our fallen soldiers. A good solid mod to take your mind off of things and simply remember. I can't really write much else here, just play it!

_data.title: Memories of Nothing
_data.description: What is this mod about?This is a romance mod featuring best girl- Natsuki!There is a good ending!Comedy!Other things.

_data.title: Mercy
_data.description: The  story  (to use the most charitable descriptor available) consists largely of MC and Sayori getting up to repetitive, almost invariably NSFW antics with only the loosest of continuity tying it all together. On rare occasions Sayori comes close to her canon characterization, but these are just brief moments of sanity. With the occasional memes and references to other mods, it could be assumed that this is meant to be comedy.Recommendation: Play in a social setting and watch people's reactions!WARNING: Quitting this mod may require the use of external help (e.g.: Task Manager on Windows)

_data.title: Murder Case
_data.description: Our usual beloved cast is featured in this story  and one by one they get taken out of the picture. But who could be behind these horrific deeds?Murder Case is a rather unique mod that features an impressive amount of choices, with an equally impressive array of endings, of which there are several. While it is apparent that the mod author's primary language is not English, the story and visuals speak for themselves. If you can look past these minor flaws, then get ready for a thrilling murder mystery!

_data.title: My Escape
_data.description: A somber tale focusing on everyone's favorite pink-haired tsundere, Natsuki. The story is an emotional thrill ride from beginning to end. Along with Natsuki herself, the rest of the literature club faces serious changes and dilemmas that tie-in to the main story. With an emotional, romantic, and heart-wrenching story, along with new backgrounds, you are sure to feel every moment of My Escape's impactful journey. My Escape deals with heavy topics and dark themes, so make sure you have some tissues on the side.

_data.title: Natsuki's Expanded Story
_data.description: In an alternate universe, you've been best friends with Natsuki since the start of High School. However, there seems to be something she isn't telling you... Will you help her escape the hand of the fate she has been dealt?

_data.title: Never Ending Tomorrow
_data.description: Author's description:You, as the protagonist of this story will have to face difficult decisions. A former entity speaks to you, warning you of future events. It's not who you think it is. As mystery fills the air you will have to choose one, or lose all. What will you do? Will you save the one you love the most, or lose all?

_data.title: New Blood
_data.description: In an unfamiliar reality, where our protagonist is an outsider, and has no prior relationships, how will he cope after being thrown into the world of the Literature Club? How will he cope, having to build relationships from scratch? Will he manage to forge new friendships, or will he be forced to continue his life, alone...Includes the DLC titled "Blood Rush".

_data.title: New Eyes
_data.description: At first, I only thought it would be temporary.However, soon, things started getting weirder and weirder. Whenever he was around, my heart would beat faster, and I wouldn't control my body anymore. There's nothing wrong with that  Right? Doki Doki! New Eyes is a fan game that lets you play through Act 1 & 2 of the original DDLC game  Through Yuri's point of view. What you see isn't necessarily what's real. Sometimes, you need to change your perspective a little  You need to look at the world with new eyes.

_data.title: New Friends Act One
_data.description: Author's description:Sayori, Yuri, and Natsuki struggle with problems that anyone could realistically struggle with. Monika, however, deals with the existential crisis that comes with being self-aware in a game. What I want to do with Doki Doki New Friends is tell a story about Monika where she doesn't struggle with such a "meta" problem. Instead, Monika struggles with obsessive-compulsive disorder and intrusive thoughts. On top of that, she has moved to a new school and as the title might imply has to make new friends. Follow Monika as she not only battles with her inner demons but also struggles with the challenges that come with making and keeping friends.

_data.title: New World
_data.description: When you decide to return to the deleted game... You understand that somebody needs your help.

_data.title: No Happiness
_data.description: One random morning, our protagonist is met with his dear friend sayori, and is offered a place, in the new Literature Club! For someone like the protagonist, this is an offer he really can't refuse. That being said, he can't shake this feeling of deja vu... then again, how could it get any worse?

_data.title: One Last Memory
_data.description: The story takes place after the original act one of Doki Doki Literature Club. Follow the emotional tale of four friends as they deal with the loss of a very important friend. Sayori, the vice president of the Literature club was taken from them in one of the worst ways anybody could ever imagine.How will our protagonist cope with this loss? How will he handle the immeasurable amount of guilt he feels after not giving his best friend enough care and attention?Will his friends be able to help? Or will they just add on to the burden of trying to recover from this loss?

_data.title: Other Clubs
_data.description: What if Monika was wrong, and they aren't *just* a game. What if Sayori was useful in surprising ways. What if Natsuki and Yuri had much more to them? Discover more about the way our world and theirs work together!

_data.title: Our Castle Walls
_data.description: In this story, where Monika is just the popular school girl instead of being self-aware, the protagonist has very high functioning autism (Asperger's Syndrome), gets convinced by Sayori, who was never his childhood friend, to consider the literature club, and he meets the other girls. Him and Yuri find out how similar they are and get to know each other as they spend more time together.

_data.title: Onii-chan Club
_data.description: Set in an alternate universe where the dokis are part of your family, they are your sisters. Thus, the usual dynamic of DDLC is changed completely in a new story where you will have to help your sisters overcome their deepest insecurities in a way to not let them fall into bullying or suicide. Note that this is not a romance mod, it's entirely focus on realism and it tries to stop the usual 'love story' plot.

_data.title: Our Final Heartbeat
_data.description: This mod provides a different ending to the game. This ending will become available after you collected all of the artworks played until the credits roll. Only then will it start.This has been made with all our love and care for the game, and as a thanks for the experience it has given to me. As a side note, I'm not natively English, so there might be some errors here and there. I'm accepting any kind of feedback, whether it's good or bad, because I want to improve myself, for the sake of this and for the sake of my future releases, if any.You'll know the installation of the mod worked if the game's title has three exclamation marks, and the version number in the Settings window has (mo) added to it. This was made for the standalone PC version, so expect the exclusive steam stuff to not happen.With love and care, NNDanny.Editor's notes: The current version of this mod contains a few bugs that can be ignored by clicking the "Ignore" button. Additionally, you can turn on "Skip unseen text" on the Settings screen to skip over dialogue while collecting the artworks necessary for the good ending. Lastly, the length of the mod was determined based on a playthrough where the standard DDLC content is skipped.

_data.title: Our Reality
_data.description: The story takes place after Monika deleted the game. The game loads and you're now in the empty classroom where you were it was just Monika and you. However, our protagonist is now the club president, thus allowing him access to the console. He brings back all of the girls and after a while the decision is made to start anew. The choice is yours. Will you use your new powers wisely? Or will you let it all go to hell?

_data.title: Our Time
_data.description: Following the bitter ending of the original game, you can make Monika return. This time around, you can finally give her the happiness that she wanted all along. In an alternate timeline split from the original story, you can finally end up with Monika. Fall in love with her all over again in a sweet, romantic, and touching story.Featuring new artworks and locations, Our Time is the perfect mod for anyone who wanted Just Monika.

_data.title: Outbreak: Red Sky
_data.description: The prelude to the story of Outbreak; a DDLC story set in zombie-infested Japan.Choose from one of two stories: Adventure, a more action-driven experience with a heavier focus on character relationships and Nightmare, a horror/drama focused narrative.. In this chapter, witness the stories of Daichi, the confident, laid-back acquaintance of MC, and Kai, the cold, sociopathic antagonist of Nightmare mode.Play through the experiences of our expanded cast of characters, as they lay the groundwork for the story to come!

_data.title: Outcast
_data.description: A Yuri-centered mod that aims to give her an interesting story and a satisfying conclusion based on the decisions you make! It will delve more into Yuri's character and give you a better understanding of who she might have been had she not been controlled or manipulated by Monika. Ultimately, it will be up to you how the story will play out.Will you help Yuri with her struggles or will she remain an outcast?

_data.title: Pantomime Show
_data.description: It's festival time, but there's a twist! Join the literature club on a lighthearted musical adventure and watch your favorite Doki perform your favorite songs! (Maybe...)Enjoy six performances, two endings, and a bonus scene! I hope you have fun attending the Doki Doki Pantomime Show!

_data.title: Pink Eyes
_data.description: in Pink Eyes, We Are Again at the club, but this time we bring Natsuki to life in this fun and warm love storyEditor's note: Some errors in Ren'Py games can be skipped by clicking Ignore.

_data.title: President Natsuki
_data.description: What if after the events of the main game, Natsuki became president? What will happen to the literature club? Will she convince everyone that manga is literature?Maybe now, you can spend time with me...

_data.title: Purist
_data.description: "Vanilla DDLC was far from the visual novel experience that we expected. As great and impactful as it was, maybe it just wasn't what you were looking for? Maybe you just wanted the traditional visual novel experience?Well, look no further than Purist! This mod turns DDLC into a traditional visual novel with 11+ hours of new content spread across four routes! Featuring new and carefully crafted artwork along with a brand new OST and more, Purist is the definitive DDLC visual novel experience!"

_data.title: Re:Coded
_data.description: A fan-made game that takes place immediately following the events of Act 4 in the main game. Monika restores what she can of the game's broken code, but doesn't have the ability to restore it fully. She instead gives the player a chance to do so, hoping that by making the right choices, everything will return to the way it once was.You'll have many choices, and each choice will impact the story. Each Doki gets their own route with branching dialogue and multiple endings. By the end, you will either have restored the Literature Club to its original state, or let it all fall apart once more.

_data.title: Relapse
_data.description: What if you knew about something horrible and had the power to prevent it from happening? Doki Doki Relapse is a story filled with humor and emotion, following a semi-sentient protagonist as he attempts to prevent a horrible event from occuring. All the while, he is faced and impeded with numerous other situations involving everybody's favorite literature club! Romance, comedy, and bitter elements all serve to make Relapse's lengthy story a rollercoaster of an experience.

_data.title: Return to the Portrait
_data.description: This mod continues straight from the end of the original game and involves everyone working together to find out the truth about their world and about Project Libitina. It features a ton of file tampering and other meta stuff like exploring the rules behind Club President powers. It also features Natsuki's dad, who is not a sadistic prick, and tries to give each character some limelight.The install process is a bit more complicated than usual. The upload URL is for the PC distribution. See here for an explanation.

_data.title: Rhapsody
_data.description: An experimental music video mod that is like a crossover between Sony Vegas and Renpy. Watch as the dokis sing Queen's famous song "Bohemian Rhapsody"!

_data.title: Rising Storm
_data.description: After joining the literature club and making friends with it's members, a presidential announcement occurs. You open your phone to check the news  and see the president announcing that we have declared war on Vietnam, and that all men 17 and older will be drafted. Your heart sinks.A few days later, you say goodbye to the literature club members and  promise them you'll make it back. Then you're off to Vietnam, unaware of the unforeseen consequences ahead of you.

_data.title: Rising Storm 2
_data.description: After waking up from a month-long coma induced by an almost fatal helicopter crash, the Main Character is only concerned about one thing: Making sure his friends at the Literature Club are okay. When he is let out of the hospital and makes his way home, he realizes that not everything is the same. His personality has drastically changed due to the experiences underwent in the war. He suffers from Post Traumatic Stress Disorder. How will it effect his relationship with his friends in the Literature Club? How will it effect his relationship with his girlfriend Yuri? How will his life be changed from these events?

_data.title: RPG
_data.description: When tragedy strikes the club, you must find the truth! This story revolves around a murder investigation, so you must find clues and dig further into what really happened. Can you put together all the pieces?Editor's note: this is a standalone fan game. You don't need to mod DDLC to play it.

_data.title: Salvation
_data.description: What if things could be different? What if you could save her? This question plagued the minds of most people after finishing the first act of DDLC. Salvation goes on to answer this question. After narrowly avoiding one tragedy, the members of the club get into an accident. Monika is forced to stay at the hospital and Sayori has to take up the mantle of club president in her absence. However, as you grow closer to the other girls Monika has to realize a dark truth. How far are you willing to go to save them? Do you have what it takes to be her Salvation?

_data.title: Sans in DDLC
_data.description: A pretty ravishing and hilarious mod with many complex animations like my previous mod. In this mod you get to play as a smiley trashbag,  witness smooth animations, explosions, and much more!You're gonna have a bad good time.

_data.title: Save Sayori
_data.description: Author's description:This is the teaser version of the fanmade "Save Sayori" mod. I already told you what the mod is about in the title.

_data.title: Savior of Souls
_data.description: We return to the Literature Club, but this time, the MC has a chance to save them all.

_data.title: Sayonara: Dreams of Letting Go Prologue
_data.description: After the tragic suicide of Sayori and a subsequent traffic accident, our protagonist is transported several years into the past where he appears to relive his childhood alongside his best friend Sayori. With vague memories of what's to come, our protagonist must find a way to manipulate the past to overcome the inevitability of his best friend's death. All the while a certain someone observes from beyond.

_data.title: Sayori Date!
_data.description: Sayori Date is a wonderful, short little mod about taking Sayori on a nice and wholesome date! If you want a super sweet mod with absolutely no demon rituals or references to Cthulhu, then you should 100% play this mod! Sayori is best girl! 100% the best! Never doubt that!

_data.title: Sayori Shoots Up The Literature Club
_data.description: Have you ever wondered what would happen if instead of committing suicide Sayori shot up the school instead?Of course you have! Lucky for you, you don't have to wait any longer because this mod offers just that. Watch as Sayori blows away the club members with her new poem, a sawed off shotgun, and prepare for a good time with a mod that finally has the 3 Gs of fun: girls, giggles, and guns.

_data.title: Scattered Stars
_data.description: This story of two siblings begins at a high school. Arito, who has made himself an outcast and Monika who is desperately trying to keep her brother in line while also managing the literature club. With the appearance of a mysterious, purple-haired girl a series of harsh ordeals awaits these two along with their friends.

_data.title: Second Chances
_data.description: Within this mod you'll find an episodic story showcasing the somber backstories of all four girls before they joined the Literature Club. Watch as all four heroines tell the ups and downs of their lives through happiness, sorrow, and anger.Editor's note: you will need to delete 'scripts.rpa' in DDLC's game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: shattered world
_data.description: Not to be confused with the less popular Shattered Worlds saga,  shattered world  (lowercase emphasized) is a heart-racing tale of action & sacrifice, stemming from Monika's newfound desire to change the Doki's lives for the better. Take back control of the protagonist, and with Monika's help you have the opportunity to save Sayori, Yuri and Natsuki in this choice-oriented masterpiece of design!Editor's note:  if you're still not sold, you get to punch Natsuki's dad in the balls.

_data.title: Somnium
_data.description: What is this mod about?facing your fearsdiscovering the truth

_data.title: Spark of Hope
_data.description: The MC finds himself in a void where he realizes there can be happiness in this world, however he can't do it without the girls. He finds away to bring back Monika and convinces her to restore the game, but at a cost. The others remember exactly what happened in the past, it's up to you to make things right again. Will you be able to rebuild the friendship they had before or will it all go horrible like the past?

_data.title: SNAFU
_data.description: This mod is a blend between comedy and seriousness (without the memes or obvious references seen in Relapse). The story follows a redesigned protagonist and his experience joining the club. By redesign, I mean he was given a personality different to the base game, as well as a past that will play into his general outlook and interactions with the dokis. He's sort of a blend between the personalities of the protagonists from these stories: "My Teen Romantic Comedy SNAFU," "Bunny-Girl Senpai," and "The Fruit of Grisaia." I've never played the mod "Fruits of the Literature Club", so there may be a slight overlap due to our similar inspirations, but if there is it will likely be negligible. With that explained, what about the game-play?There will be 10~11 'routes' available, though that doesn't mean you'll have to play through the mod that many times. Each girl has two routes, a lover route and a friend route. You can only do one lover route at a time (so no harem), but you could technically clear multiple friend routes in a single playthrough. To give an idea, it's a similar system to what you would see in a Persona game.Two new characters are also introduced (hence the 10~11 routes), but one of them is totally optional if new characters aren't your thing.The potential of a stat system exists. Again, this is a similar system to what you'd see in a Persona game, with there being four "stats" that can be raised to unlock new scenes and interactions. It's currently incorporated into the code and present in the demo, but it may be removed or altered in the future if I run out of ways to use it meaningfully.But why don't you see all these for yourself? Click below to download the demo!

_data.title: Starry-Eyed
_data.description: A short, lighthearted mod; perfect for a quick dose of doki.Sayori and MC are in a relationship before MC joins the literature club, but lately there's been a little trouble in paradise. And when Monika shows up at MC's place to vent her troubles, misunderstandings are bound to happen.Will they patch things over? What do Yuri and Natsuki think of all this? Find out in this short, sitcom-esque DDLC mod!

_data.title: Summer Hope
_data.description: Prepare to delve into the heartwarming story of Summer Hope, which follows the blossoming love between the protagonist and, of course, our favorite tsundere! A must-play for Natsuki lovers, the mod features a lengthy story that encompasses romance, tragedy, and hope, complimented by several custom backgrounds and character artworks with a unique, carefully crafted art style.

_data.title: Sunny Rains
_data.description: Watch as the club is formed from the ground up in the perspective of one of the main girls from the original game and how their bounds were formed through this mod.

_data.title: Sweet Dreams
_data.description: What if you had someone who loves you for who you are; someone who you'd want to spend your entire life with. Must be a sweet dream to have such a thing. I wish to never awaken from it.

_data.title: Switcheroo
_data.description: Doki Doki with a twist! Featuring brand new sprites, new music, and (technically) new characters, play as a female protagonist as you try to win over your favorite Doki in a genderbent literature club!Now, there's not really a ton I can say for Switcheroo considering it's pretty much the vanilla game built around the genderbent gimmick, but I fixed and rewrote what I could

_data.title: Take Two
_data.description: A sequel mod that expands on the story of the original game. After a brief chat in the void, Monika and Sayori decide to give their world one last chance. Now armed with the knowledge that all the club members are sentient, a better result is all they can hope for. Sayori also retains her self-awareness, so Monika is a little less alone this time.The demo contains all of  Act 5.  It begins on the day of the festival, introduces two new characters, and proceeds from there with routes for everyone. It's structure is similar to Act 1 of the first game, but very little of the original is reused (unless you don't listen to Monika at the start, ahaha).The first playthrough is roughly two hours long. Skipping repeated scenes leaves each route at an hour or so each. Although this demo consists of Act 5 in its entirety, there is still a lot more to look forward to. Act 6 shifts the game into a linear story with plenty of intrigue and unexpected twists. The next release will be the full version, but it may take a long time to develop.

_data.title: The Binding of Isaac Mod
_data.description: Were you a fan of the darker aspects of the original game? Have you wondered how the girls would fare in a more hostile world? Are you up for an action-packed adventures the girl of your choice? If so, you've come to the right place. Join our favourite club members in this gruesome crossover made for The Binding of Isaac!FeaturesAll 4 Playable Dokis with 4 unique Transformations!2 New Active Items!4 New Passive Items!Custom Sound Effects!Costume compatibility with Rebirth/Afterbirth items....SecretsEditor's note: this is not a mod for Doki Doki Literature Club. It was made for The Binding of Isaac: Afterbirth+ and you need to have that game to play this mod.

_data.title: The Blood Moon Chapters: Chapter 1 - Before, During and After the Stories
_data.description: "Billions of years ago on a distant realm much different from ours, a great war caused by a great demon of the void raged throughout the realm. His forces travelled the cosmos, destroying everything in it's path, leaving nothing in it's wake. Without the protection from the realm's guardians that had long since fallen after their inevitable defeat against this Demonlord, the realm began to fall into a dark era. Knowing that everything would soon perish from the Demon's power, the realm's denizens escaped to the other realms seeking refuge from the wages of war of their own realm. Among these survivors... two half-brothers escaped into our world. One of them would meet with Destiny once more..."Blood Moon  based on the concept of 'Project Libitina' and expands upon it. It also adds its own touches to plot holes that were never present to begin with. It's more of a lore-based chapter, as well as showing us the origins of the girls that are now the Dokis we know and love.Blood Moon is a rather unique DDLC mod. Instead of re-using all the assets from the base game, it presents a new cast of characters, a new soundtrack, and brand new locations. Some are based on real locations: like the nuclear plant of Chernobyl or the city of Las Vegas. Then there's locations from other games like Big Mountain from Fallout: New Vegas: Old World Blues.Editor's note: This is an early access demo release. Please take that into consideration.

_data.title: The Festival
_data.description: Picking up where the original game went wrong (the end of Act I), this mod fixes its problems and takes you to where you could never go before: The Festival. Join Sayori, Natsuki, Yuri, and Monika in a new adventure spanning an entire week. Read new poems, try all four routes and meet the new member!If you're confused on what to do, check out the official guide.The mod has currently only been tested on Windows and Mac. If you need a bit of help, please join the Discord server. You can also find a guide there to get the good ending... check the #good-ending chat ;)Editor's note: While it is essentially the full version, there are still a few mistakes and some known problems that have yet to be fixed.

_data.title: The Fruits of the Literature Club
_data.description: UPDATE: This is the full release for Fruits of the Literature Club containing all five chapters for all the routes.Prepare to partake in a thrilling adventure alongside a new main character whose past is shrouded in mystery! You are given the choice of picking one from the four sweet fruits of the Literature Club. Each route has dramatic twists in store and tells a different side of the protagonist's backstory. This action-packed rollercoaster of a mod is not for the faint of heart. It will keep you on the edge of your seat with it's immersive narration and dialogue.But, after all is said and done  The seeds of their future, are sewn in his past.

_data.title: The Good Ending
_data.description: Our beloved protagonist has awoken to the true nature of his reality. Whether he's ready for it or not, he is the only one who has the power to save everyone. Joining the Literature Club for the second time isn't easy. How do you face the friends you watched die, knowing they won't remember a second of it?Help MC as he explores his new reality and does whatever he can to set things right. He can't do it alone   but at least he has you.

_data.title: The Musical
_data.description: This mod is a playable version of the music video "Just Monika" by Random Encounters. Meaning it plays like a normal mod but also has musical elements embedded in it. It was recently overhauled to have a new extended story and brand new features, such as updated sprites and backgrounds, grammatical error fixes, and much much more. [25th June 2020]

_data.title: The New Literature Club
_data.description: A grand idea inspired this mod: what about a full-blown sequel to DDLC?The story takes place after the good ending of DDLC, with a self-aware Sayori thanking you for all you did (while Monika floats out in limbo after her deletion). Set two months after this event, our protagonist returns to the literature club after having drifted away from it to find a larger group of 7, now. He finds all three of the girls (Natsuki, Yuri, and of course, Sayori) in the club cute, and this sways him to join. Now, he must help the club get ready for the upcoming Winter Festival, all while trying to impress the girl of his fancy.This game will expand a lot of the features of DDLC. There is still poem writing, still drama between the club members, and still all the loveable quirks in the dialogue. However, this game will be much larger. Act 1 has 5 ways to end (though this trickles into only 3 distinct ways to play through Act 2). There are four new male characters, each with distinct personalities and ties to the Doki girls we know and love. It tackles how Sayori might deal with her self-awareness, in light of her depression, and also asks what the club would be like if it were larger. I won't delve too much further into detail, I'll let that be left for later.

_data.title: The Perfect Story
_data.description: You are put into the shoes of a young man who has played DDLC many times over. He wished he could save the girls from their demise. On a fateful day he is miraculously transported into their world and is tasked with a quest. Will he meet the demands of this all-powerful being? Come and find out how The Perfect Story unfolds!

_data.title: The Post Credit Scene
_data.description: What if DDLC had a special scene at the end teasing a potential sequel? this is merely a what if scenario with a lil meta humor. you don't need to replay the entire game again to see the scene just replace the files as you do with other mods and just start a new game! if you have a minute or 2 to spare then this is the mod for you!

_data.title: The Yuri Parable
_data.description: Do you like the The Stanley Parable? Do you like Doki Doki Literature Club? Have you ever wished that the two games would crossover? Do you like tedious questions that are asked purely to generate intrigue? If you answered  yes  to any of the prior questions, you are in luck!The Yuri Parable is an experience for those looking for a comedic adventure focused around a certain pen-loving bookworm (cough cough Yuri cough cough), alongside a very handsome narrator. The Yuri Parable does not assume any fault nor can it be sued for any  terrible jokes  it might produce.

_data.title: Thot Club
_data.description: Instead of thinking about what it would be like if MC saved the dokis, why not wonder what it would be like if MC hated them? Speaking of MC, what if he was an All American boi that had some very strong political (Conservative) beliefs? Well, we answer these questions with Doki Doki Thot Club, because the club is filled with hella thots. (We have a very mutual respect for our beloved dokis, which brings us to say that no dokis were harmed during the making of this mod, .--- -.-)Also, this mod is pretty NSFW in some ways, and some of the views that are presented in this mod can be offensive to some people. This mod, by no means should be taken seriously. Overall it should be taken as a joke.

_data.title: The Portrait of Markov
_data.description: The Portrait of Markov is a spin on the normal DDLC storyline where instead of focusing on the Dokis, you focus on Libitina. Follow her around as she discovers her past containing many dark secrets, sad moments, and more. The ultimate goal of the mod is to show a story never seen before in Doki mods.Current version: 1.0 [18th August 2020]

_data.title: Through Time and Space
_data.description: Author's description:What would you do if you could travel through time and space with the click of a button?

_data.title: Time to be an epic hero
_data.description: Prepare for RPG like tale in Doki Doki universe. You will need to first help your favourite anime girls with their problems caused by a mysterious entity operating behind the scenes. Find out who he is and take him down. Be ware that girls may die depending on how you play. Excited? You should be.Last updated: 9th June 2020

_data.title: Total Fold
_data.description: This mod was made as part of a short mod challenge hosted by u/chiffmonkey, where the point was to make a mod using only the assets available in a supplied folder with specific assets. And of course, to make a story that made sense. While a few things were added majority of the assets came from chiffmonkey's folder.Enjoy our protagonist's reminiscence over his highschool years.

_data.title: True Feelings
_data.description: Author's description:It'll be about Monika telling her True Feelings towards the MC. It will be a short Mod and will hopefully be released by mid June 2020 (hopefully)..

_data.title: True Happiness
_data.description: The story starts off with our protagonist not remembering any of the club members. As he starts regaining his memories, he finds a purpose: to save all of the girls of the literature club! Will he be able to overcome the challenges he has to face? Will you find a bitter or a sweet ending? Play it for yourself and find out!

_data.title: True World
_data.description: Monika  not only brought back the girls, she even managed to bring them into your reality! What will you do when you cross paths on your side of the screen?

_data.title: Tutorial!
_data.description: A mod that finally gives a proper tutorial for upcoming modders, expanding on the Modding Template and the subreddit's modding tutorial. What do you mean that's not what the mod's about? Did I miss something?

_data.title: Twin Realities
_data.description: In DDLC Twin Realities, you play as a NEET, like Sayori would say. You're a nerd, a loner, an outcast- who's about to change his life. After Monika put you in her space room you refused to delete her. Instead, you wrote mod after mod to spend time with Monika. Monika is controlled by an intelligent AI and she can react to things that happen by herself. In each mod you write dialogue for MC, so that he can react, talk, and have fun with Monika. But it never felt real.Until now.Your dad received a mysterious package from your late uncle. He was a great inventor who died before he could finish his inventions. Your dad decides to leave for the week and throw the things away later, but you know better. With your technology skills you manage to finish a most peculiar device nicknamed the Reality Machine: Made to transport people to and from a virtual world. Here is your plan. You are going inside DDLC, build four copies of the machine in the game, and let the girls use the device to come to your reality.

_data.title: Ultimate Combo
_data.description: Ever wanted to play ComboDev's mod on your own? Well, now, you can! You'll be able to play the old and new mods anytime!Editor's note: Since this is a compilation of many mods, it's mixed genre-wise. Alongside romance you'll find comedy, horror and serious drama within this mod.Please read the content warning section before playing.

_data.title: Undone Fate
_data.description: When Monika retains her memories of the previous playthrough, events go down differently than in the base game. How differently? Well, the inclusion of a whole new week to play through for starters! But be warned: Just because Monika is no longer messing with the game's code doesn't mean there are no more tragedies that can go down in the Literature Club... Can you Undo the tragic Fate this game is pushing for and ensure a happy ending?Editor's note: The beginning of this mod is mostly the same as Act 1 of DDLC, albeit with minor changes.

_data.title: Vigilante
_data.description: This mod is about a highschool boy who moves back into his childhood neighbourhood after 5 years. Just as he settles into his surroundings, he is granted a special power that he must carry responsibly.Includes demo for Chapter 2.

_data.title: We are the Literature Club
_data.description: This story was created to continue on the story of the Literature Club, and to give the girls the ending that they deserved, as well as the closure that the player thought they would never get.Set in an alternate canon, where the meddlings of the class president never took place, We are the Literature Club carries on the story by laying a new foundation in storytelling, eventually culminating in the revival of the Literature Club for a new era.With a small cast of new characters, and familiar ones, We are the Literature Club sets the stage for an enjoyable "re-write" of the world of Doki Doki Literature Club, with a slight twist in an alternate timeline.After all that happened; are you really willing to let it end there?"

_data.title: We are the Literature Club II
_data.description: A parody of Rockstar Games' Red Dead Redemption II in DDLC's style, bringing to life a new arc in We Are The Literature Club's story. Set during a heavily competitive festival revolving around literature (in which the whole town is in on), the Literature Club does everything in their power to collect the most literature out of all the attending clubs. This leads to the club president doing everything she can to win, which sometimes results in her ambition getting the best of her. Caught in the crossfire is our protagonist, who is trying to make the best of the situation.It falls on you to help him make the right choices. Will you be able to help the other club members cope, or focus on more selfish means to resolve the conflicts that arise?

_data.title: Weatheard World
_data.description: A story revolving around the club president Monika, and her drive to create a new world. A new world for her, and for You, the player. But this decision must be made wisely, as sacrifices will be warranted. Just how big of a sacrifice is needed?But perhaps  maybe Monika isn't the one pulling all of the strings now?Editor's note: Please, take this mod with a pinch of salt  and a bag of pop corn.

_data.title: West Virginia Club
_data.description: This mod was supposed to have a story focused on West Virginian issues and made comedic light and commentary on them. Such as teen pregnancy, drug addiction, incest, and the KKK. As of now, the game had all of act one rewritten, a festival added, and a good 1/3rd of Monika's route written and coded.Notes from the author: link. (only read after you played the mod)Editor's note: You'll need to delete 'scripts.rpa' from your game folder before running this mod.

_data.title: Window to Your Heart
_data.description: In Window to Your Heart, you play a brand new MC: a transfer student cursed with a special gift. This mod takes place after an alternate version of DDLC's Act 1, leading to the dissolution of the literature club. At Monika's request, it's your job to reform the club as well as the girls' friendship before graduation.

_data.title: World of Dreams
_data.description: A certain player (With a first and last name so keep that in mind when naming your character) is thrust into the world of Doki Doki Literature Club. He finds himself possessing the body of the game's protagonist, Meiji Chizu. However, Meiji is still around, just relegated to backseat driver in his own body. Together, along with Monika, they try to prevent the events of the original game from happening. Will they succeed? Or will they fail? And remember, the game doesn't end...until the credits are over.

_data.title: Yandere Club
_data.description: Your childhood friend, Sayori invites you to the Literature Club. However, the next day you notice something's off about the girls. They became absolutely obsessed over you! It's like your dreams came true, but it's more than you bargained for. Can you find out what happened to them? Better yet... can you survive their rabid love-craze?

_data.title: Yandere Madness
_data.description: After Maltese Insanity, with Black Scientist trapped in the void from G-Man; Monika in her spaceroom, and the dokis brought back to DDLC with memories of what happened erased and the MC reset (And Daniel remaining trapped in the game). Everything was going normal in DDLC, with Daniel calling the girls thots. Until... one day.... the dokis were acting strange, enough to even make the dense MC worry. With the girls finally snapping mentally and turning into full blown yanderes while the MC finds himself in a strange new world, what horrifying things will the MC along with Black Scientist and Daniel face? Will the mystery lingering behind the scenes finally get solved once and for all?Find out in this mod!

_data.title: Youtuber Club
_data.description: Author's description:This is a short comedic mod about the Dokis (and MC) becoming youtubers because Monika wants to try something new.

_data.title: Yuri Reality
_data.description: You're put in the shoes of a typical guy who joins the Literature Club. Things gradually spiral out of control. He has to choose between two of the most attractive club members, but is there something darker at hand?
